<h1>NIPS &rsquo;13 Workshop on Crowdsourcing: Theory, Algorithms and Applications</h1>
<div id="subtitle"><br />
Workshop in conjunction with <a href="http://nips.cc/Conferences/2013/">NIPS</a> 2013. </div>
</div>
<div class="infoblock">
<div class="blockcontent">
